上传镜像</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#2-6-%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BA%E5%92%8C%E8%BD%BD%E5%85%A5%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F"><span class="toc-number">2.6.</span> <span class="toc-text">2.6 导出和载入镜像</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#2-7-%E7%A7%BB%E9%99%A4%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F"><span class="toc-number">2.7.</span> <span class="toc-text">2.7 移除本地镜像</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E4%B8%89%E3%80%81%E5%AE%B9%E5%99%A8"><span class="toc-number">3.</span> <span class="toc-text">三、容器</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#3-1-%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D"><span class="toc-number">3.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">3.1 介绍</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#3-2-%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%B9%E5%99%A8"><span class="toc-number">3.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">3.2 创建容器</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#3-3-%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E5%AE%B9%E5%99%A8"><span class="toc-number">3.3.</span> <span class="toc-text">3.3 启动容器</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#3-4-%E5%AE%88%E6%8A%A4%E6%80%81%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C"><span class="toc-number">3.4.</span> <span class="toc-text">3.4 守护态运行</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#3-5-%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5%E5%AE%B9%E5%99%A8"><span class="toc-number">3.5.</span> <span class="toc-text">3.5 进入容器</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#3-6-%E7%BB%88%E6%AD%A2%E5%AE%B9%E5%99%A8"><span class="toc-number">3.6.</span> <span class="toc-text">3.6 终止容器</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#3-7-%E5%B0%86%E5%AE%B9%E5%99%A8%E4%BF%9D%E5%AD%98%E4%B8%BA%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F"><span class="toc-number">3.7.</span> <span class="toc-text">3.7 将容器保存为镜像</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc